prefetchAd() - Method in class com.mahmud.widespacesdktest.AdSpace
The prefetchAd method will act almost same as the runAd method, but only difference is that it will store its callbacks into a queue.If a user calls prefetchAd method then the prefetch callbacks will be fired sequentially after the provisioner is completed.so that we post every prefetch runnable in a handler.In runnable run method it's check the provision status by checkProvisionStatus and post the listener in a handler.
provision() - Method in class com.mahmud.widespacesdktest.Provisioner
This method is used for provisioning.First it get the server url by getServerUrl(URL) method.URL is a constant key string.If the url is not null then it sent to HTTP request by sendHttpRequest(url) method.Otherwise it's change the provision status ENUM value as FAILED.
Provisioner - Class in com.mahmud.widespacesdktest
This class demonstrates to contact with server side to make sure the provision status and notify with all listener.It's implement two interface class to notify the other listener and another interface using to add and remove listener with this provision.
